title: Alex.Jones.Show.2008.06.13-chakra71
description:
Friday 06-13
Keith Byrne of We Are Change Ireland returns to talk about the Irish Lisbon Treaty referendum. Member of the United States House of Representatives Dennis Kucinich talks about his articles of impeachment. Barbara Lowe Fisher of the National Vaccine Information Center talks about the dangers of childhood vaccines. Ralph Nader, David Edwards, Paul Watson, Mark Dice, and Jesse Benton make appearances. 

Sourced from infowars podcast.  Four hours before commercial edit takes it down to 3 hours.
